OL,3,CAspiring Chief Minister slams move to
OL,4,Cpublish accounts after election
OL,6,FOne of the candidates vying to become
OL,7,FGuernsey's next President of Policy
OL,8,Fand Resources says not seeing the full
OL,9,Fstate of the island's finances ahead
OL,10,Fof the General Election has damaged
OL,11,Fthe democratic process.
OL,13,FDeputy Charles Parkinson, who finished
OL,14,Fthird in the poll, says the complete
OL,15,FStates' accounts for last year should
OL,16,Fhave been made a matter of public
OL,17,Frecord before the election, so voters
OL,18,Fcould have been better informed.
