OL,3,CAspiring Chief Minister slams move to
OL,4,Cpublish accounts after election
OL,6,FHe explains: "I think the States'
OL,7,Ffinances are in much better health
OL,8,Fthan we've been led to believe before
OL,9,Fthe election.
OL,11,F"We didn't see the 2024 accounts
OL,12,Fbefore the General Election, which was
OL,13,Fa severe blow to the democratic
OL,14,Fprocess."
OL,16,FThe States of Guernsey says deputies
OL,17,Fin the previous Assembly voted to
OL,18,Fpublish the accounts on this date.
