OL,3,CAspiring Chief Minister slams move to
OL,4,Cpublish accounts after election
OL,6,FDeputy Jonathan Le Tocq, who is also
OL,7,Faiming to become Guernsey's next Chief
OL,8,FMinister, believes the #44 million
OL,9,Fnumber was the most important to
OL,10,Funderstand the overall financial
OL,11,Fpicture.
OL,13,FHe says: "That is the amount we need
OL,14,Ffor business as usual. This includes
OL,15,Fthe running of the hospital, schools
OL,16,Fand paying the salaries of teachers
OL,17,Fand nurses."
