OL,3,CAspiring Chief Minister slams move to
OL,4,Cpublish accounts after election
OL,6,FDeputy-elect Andy Sloan, the former
OL,7,FChief Economist for the States of
OL,8,FGuernsey and one of the 20 new States
OL,9,Fmembers, says that greater
OL,10,Ftransparency is needed in the process
OL,11,Fof publishing accounts.
OL,13,FHe adds: "I haven't seen the exact
OL,14,Ffigures yet, but they probably aren't
OL,15,Fas bad as they were claimed to be last
OL,16,FNovember.
OL,18,F"However, they're still not great and
OL,19,Fwe've got to address that deficit one
OL,20,Fway or another."
